article_title: County hospital abandons partnership talks with Vidant, CarolinaEast

article_metadata.description: Onslow Memorial Hospital abandoned plans to merge with Vidant Health and CarolinaEast after months of stalled negotiations over details about leadership at Jacksonville's independent nonprofit.
article_metadata.author: Michael Todd
